{"tid":884824,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中超賽前奏國歌捽面掩鼻　巴西前國腳被指「舉止不莊重」罰停賽","createTime":"2018-11-01T01:58:06.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-01T11:23:26.000Z","uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"1112ae5f412179dfcb851e3d386a8affc6455474","tid":884824,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T01:58:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/player_hLntc_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2Fplayer_hLntc_1200x0.png&h=822b677b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n內地傳媒報道，上周日舉行的中國足球超級聯賽，山東魯能的巴西前國腳前鋒泰廸利被指不尊重國歌，結果被中國足協判罰停賽一場。不過泰廸利其實只是心不在焉地掩一掩面，結果被中國足協指「舉止不莊重，造成不良社會影響」。<br />\n<br />\n今仗魯能作客榜首上海上港，賽前依賽規奏出中國國歌，站在隊伍最尾的泰廸利被鏡頭攝到有點心不在焉，捽捽面又掩掩鼻。魯能最終作客負2:4，終止五場不敗走勢。禍不單行的是，中國足協紀律委員會今天公佈，根據《中國足球協會紀律準則》第 104條規定，足協紀律委員會指泰廸利「舉止不莊重，造成不良社會影響」，予以停賽一場處分，立即生效。<br />\n<br />\n聲明更指中國足協會依照《中國足球協會紀律準則》的規定，「堅決嚴肅處理各類違規違紀行為，淨化賽場風氣。」<br />\n<br />\n中超聯賽只餘三輪，山東魯能現時以51分排第三，無可能超越位列榜頭兩名的上海上港及廣州恒大，球隊亦僅較北京國安領先兩分，餘下三輪必須穏住第三才可確保一席亞冠盃附加賽資格，失去今季在聯賽射入17球的泰廸利，對球隊不無影響，幸好魯能下仗主場只是對排名第十的長泰亞泰。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/china/中超賽前奏國歌捽面掩鼻-巴西前國腳被指-舉止不莊重-罰停賽/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fchina%2F%E4%B8%AD%E8%B6%85%E8%B3%BD%E5%89%8D%E5%A5%8F%E5%9C%8B%E6%AD%8C%E6%8D%BD%E9%9D%A2%E6%8E%A9%E9%BC%BB-%E5%B7%B4%E8%A5%BF%E5%89%8D%E5%9C%8B%E8%85%B3%E8%A2%AB%E6%8C%87-%E8%88%89%E6%AD%A2%E4%B8%8D%E8%8E%8A%E9%87%8D-%E7%BD%B0%E5%81%9C%E8%B3%BD%2F&d=b7DOn9OyI3Miq2JAdG7N8JZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=466b1b79\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fchina%2F%E4%B8%AD%E8%B6%85%E8%B3%BD%E5%89%8D%E5%A5%8F%E5%9C%8B%E6%AD%8C%E6%8D%BD%E9%9D%A2%E6%8E%A9%E9%BC%BB-%E5%B7%B4%E8%A5%BF%E5%89%8D%E5%9C%8B%E8%85%B3%E8%A2%AB%E6%8C%87-%E8%88%89%E6%AD%A2%E4%B8%8D%E8%8E%8A%E9%87%8D-%E7%BD%B0%E5%81%9C%E8%B3%BD%2F&h=e0f52741\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/china/中超賽前奏國歌捽面掩鼻-巴西前國腳被指-舉止不莊重-罰停賽/</a>"},{"pid":"e487de8a1f08bc2dd5a83a05f275beaaf116f5d2","tid":884824,"uid":74278,"like":0,"dislike":37,"score":-37,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T02:00:10.000Z","msg":"中立啲睇人地國家播國歌你唔使唱都要比啲尊重嘅"},{"pid":"59fbf7f099a39e2934df8736bb44e82fc77a270d","tid":884824,"uid":997,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T02:00:24.000Z","msg":"唔洗踢有糧出<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b3ece57b3ad87c4e51d30bb3b8aafca030426c6","tid":884824,"uid":13115,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T02:11:31.000Z","msg":"以後奏支歌就R屎忽<br />\n就可以R住屎忽收錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7ec998631cd69ba39424dd406e83c079488cfdc","tid":884824,"uid":19037,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T04:54:37.000Z","msg":"佢痛哭流涕先會捽面掩鼻啫"},{"pid":"9098612aff877fdc37138cdf43abfba6f0cfbf23","tid":884824,"uid":52006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T05:14:30.000Z","msg":"咁美斯世界盃果場都應該要被禁賽<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"365ce73912d213a1c57669528e93a4ed81a583ea","tid":884824,"uid":51720,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T05:18:14.000Z","msg":"🇨🇳🇭🇰❌🙈 ⭕😮"},{"pid":"d8a5f236a0de0b42fb9b923ceb8e736b507172b5","tid":884824,"uid":28913,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T10:13:58.000Z","msg":"玻璃心廢柴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0cddcfa36ecd927ce50e8bbeaa80e6c38569ef1","tid":884824,"uid":14715,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T10:17:06.000Z","msg":"你唔尊重公司<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 罰你放有薪假一天<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d08fd2ffca0d4b2c46d2974d29a454ea728fd9d9","tid":884824,"uid":135753,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTi